Hello Medford residents, I'm Patrick Clerken, a candidate for one of seven seats on our City Council. I intend to restore reason, balance, and trust back to our governance and community. Alongside this basic promise of civil and open-minded character, I am providing dozens of testimonials from those who know me in my professional, civic, and private life.

