00:01:11,311 --> 00:01:36,505
whether geographic, like particular wards, demographic, like particular generational and economic groupings, or ideological, like partisan leaning. They've forgotten their oath that as at-large representatives, our city councilors are meant to serve the needs of the city in its entirety, as if it were an ecosystem run on symbiotic respect. But I haven't forgotten, nor will I develop this peculiar amnesia.

